---

## ‚úÖ CLI Usage

Run from terminal:

```bash
floodrisk --aoi Feni --before_start 2025-01-01 --before_end 2025-01-31 --after_start 2025-07-01 --after_end 2025-07-12 --flood_raster Flood_Extent.tif --output results --visualize
```

